{"ts": "2026-06-07T21:04:15.659616+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "**Package Manager: Yarn (Classic v1)**\n\nThe repository relies on **Yarn** (the lockfile `yarn.lock` is present) and the `Taskfile.yaml` uses `yarn install`, `yarn release`, etc. Scripts in `package.json` also call `yarn lint --fix`.\n\n---\n\n### Environment‑Specific Script Names (from `package.json`)\n\n| Script | Command | Purpose |\n|---|---|---|\n| `dev` | `cross-env NODE_ENV=local vite --host` | Start local development server |\n| `dev:stg` | `cross-env NODE_ENV=stg vite` | Start staging development server |\n| `serve` | `vite preview --host` | Preview the built application |\n| `build` | `vite build --mode prod` | Build for production |\n| `build:stg` | `cross-env vite build --mode test` | Build for staging |\n| `build:prod` | `cross-env vite build --mode production` | Build for production (explicit) |\n| `deploy` | `gh-pages -d dist` | Deploy to GitHub Pages |\n| `lint` | `eslint --ext .jsx,.js,.ts,.tsx .` | Lint all source files |\n| `fix` | `yarn lint --fix` | Auto‑fix lint issues |\n\n### Environment‑Specific Env Files (in `envs/`)\n\n| File | Target Environment |\n|---|---|\n| `envs/.env.local` | Local development |\n| `envs/.env.stg` | Staging |\n| `envs/.env.prod` | Production |\n\n### How they connect\n\nThe `Taskfile.yaml`’s `init` task copies one of these env files (e.g., `cp envs/.env.local .env`) to become the active `.env` file, which Vite reads at runtime. The corresponding `NODE_ENV` and `VITE_BUILD_ENV` values in each file match the environment intended for the script (e.g., `dev` → `.env.local`, `dev:stg` → `.env.stg`, `build:prod` → `.env.prod`).", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 491, "prompt_tokens": 7311, "total_tokens": 7802, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 14, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 6912}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 6912, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 399}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-flash", "system_fingerprint": "fp_8b330d02d0_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "92132715-9dd8-42b2-a277-3d4c35e05ff4", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea3e6-7579-76c0-8ed8-29b491d0ee13-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 7311, "output_tokens": 491, "total_tokens": 7802, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 6912}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 14}}}}]}}}
